title: What Cap or Limit should we set on our Burning Mechanic?
body: This ballot is being used to determine whether we limit our burning through a hard cap on the total number OR a window of time in which burning is available. Once one of these choices is made, we will put a follow up vote up for the specifics.
choices: Hard cap on the number of Burns
author: 0xA6aE963A928bccA7f427cCe4BD66Cddd54f0fab3
